  "title": "Sales and marketing (fast pace)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>At Royal Org, we believe the people make a difference. Like clay in a potter’s hand, we continuously mould each individual by giving them room to make mistakes, opportunities to be exposed to, and grow as a family. We strongly believe in guiding, leading and walking together as a team to achieve success.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Join a dynamic team to support and execute marketing campaigns, develop practical skills, and grow your career with strong mentorship and real-world experience in a fast-paced environment.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Collaborate with team members to execute marketing campaigns that engage customers and meet brand objectives</li><li>Support the creation of memorable customer experiences through creative and strategic campaign activities</li><li>Participate in brainstorming sessions to generate ideas and solve challenges related to marketing projects</li><li>Develop communication, confidence, and leadership skills by actively contributing to team discussions and tasks</li></ul>",
